text:
Almost 7 hours of Sametori? What a blessing!
A few tips for future builds when you find yourself with a messy inventory. You can make any block you have in your inventory show up in your hand by looking at one in the world with your crosshair and clicking your mousewheel on it. So if you look at cyan wool you placed down and middle click, if you had cyan wool somewhere in your inventory, it’ll go into your hand automatically.

Also, you already know but it did seem to trip you up sometimes. Scaffolding builds up only when you click on the side of one. And it builds out to the side in the direction you're facing only when you click on the top.
